groupTitle: UGA / Athens Lease, Subleases, Roommates, Off Campus Housing & Apartments

text:
Hey there guys, I am trying to find someone to take over my lease at Polo Club for the next school year (2025-2026)!

I have lived here for a year in a 4b/b two-story apartment (fully furnished) with three other girls I hadn't known before, and it has been nothing but great. I have recently been given a life-changing opportunity, which is causing me to leave. Otherwise, I would've stayed for how wonderful it's been. You don't have to worry about spaces for parking; the buses to campus are incredibly reliable, and the Polo Club staff are genuinely the best I've ever dealt with (I've tried several other apartment complexes before this one).

The Polo Club Apartment complex is renowned for being one of the best places to live while in college, partly due to its spacious rooms, which are among the largest in Athens. Staff are always on top of maintenance orders.

The entire area is filled with activities to do, including basketball, volleyball on the sand, frisbee, a large pool with grills, a functioning fireplace beside the grills, tennis courts, and more. Truly, a lot is going on here. Location itself is amazing, it's right beside campus (especially vet) and by a bunch of stores and places to eat.

Please reach out if interested or have any questions at all!
